description: Spanish police are investigating whether a party attended by Prince Joachim breached lockdown rules.
title: Coronavirus: Belgian Prince Joachim tests positive after lockdown party
title_page: Coronavirus: Belgian Prince Joachim tests positive after lockdown party - BBC News
maintext: Spain is in the process of emerging from one of the strictest lockdowns in Europe. It outlined a four-stage plan on 4 May to start easing the lockdown, which saw children under 14 confined to their homes for six weeks.
